com.fns.grivet.model

Enum AttributeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AttributeType>
      • com.fns.grivet.model.AttributeType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<AttributeType>

    public enum AttributeType
extends Enum<AttributeType>
    An AttributeType specifies the type of an Attribute defined in a ClassAttribute. It may be declared independent from an Attribute participating in multiple ClassAttribute instances. Mediates between Java and SQL types.
    Author:
    Chris Phillipson
